      "updated": 1774965474053,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Handles development workflow end-to-end \n(from source code to build).\nTransforms source code, bundles, optimizes\nassets.",
      "fontSize": 14.69864107444901,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Handles development workflow end-to-end \n(from source code to build).\nTransforms source code, bundles, optimizes assets.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "s5d5ytOiVzc3NdMaSUyiV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -6542.915141272861,
      "y": -13698.881670714298,
