      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "On platforms like Java and C#, there’s no\nconcept of a “bundler”, only build tools (same).\nThe term “bundler” is specific to JavaScript\nand originated from JavaScript ecosystem.",
      "fontSize": 12.85759411593681,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "On platforms like Java and C#, there’s no concept of a “bundler”, only build tools (same).\nThe term “bundler” is specific to JavaScript and originated from JavaScript ecosystem.",
